{"metadata":{"name":"Sunan Ibn Majah","section":{"20":"The Chapters on Legal Punishments"}},"hadiths":[{"hadithnumber":2557,"arabicnumber":2557,"text":"২/২৫৫৭। জাবির ইবনে সামুরা (রাঃ) থেকে বর্ণিত। নবী সাল্লাল্লাহু আলাইহি ওয়াসাল্লাম একজোড়া ইহূদী নারী-পুরুষকে রজম করেছিলেন।","grades":[{"name":"Al-Albani","grade":"Sahih"},{"name":"Muhammad Fouad Abd al-Baqi","grade":"Sahih Lighairihi"},{"name":"Shuaib Al Arnaut","grade":"Sahih Lighairihi"},{"name":"Zubair Ali Zai","grade":"Hasan Or Sahih"}],"reference":{"book":20,"hadith":25}}]}